"конкретной кампании. При редакции письма, наоборот, можно менять только "
"текст писма, хедер и футер как часть шаблона менять нельзя."
msgstr ""
"When editing a template, you can change only the email header and footer. "
"The text in the email is placeholder content — during an actual send, it "
"will be replaced with the email text of the specific campaign. When editing "
"an email, on the contrary, you can change only the email text; the header "
"and footer, as part of the template, cannot be changed."

